This is shell script to run a number of vasp jobs automatically
folder of vasp jobs should have name in a sequence like 1,2,3,....
ncell value should be changed according to your no. of jobs. by default it is 24
change no of cores and path of vasp exe, as given in the following line in run.sh before running the code


mpirun -np 32 /home/iyad/vasp.5.4.4/bin/vasp_std



Input
_______
vasp folders 1,2,3,.... which contains INCAR, POSCAR, POTCAR and KPOINTS files


Process
________
./run.sh


Output
________
OUTCAR and other files for each case.
